# OpenapiClient::Account

## Properties

| Name | Type | Description | Notes |
| ---- | ---- | ----------- | ----- |
| **username** | **String** | Username of the user profile. | [optional] |
| **type** | **String** | The role of the user. | [optional] |

## Example

```ruby
require 'openapi_client'

instance = OpenapiClient::Account.new(
```
